      background-size:22px}\n\n        .z_loading {\n            position: fixed;\n            bottom: 0;\n            left: 0;\n            right: 0;\n            z-index: 100;\n            color: #999;\n            font-size: 12px;\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 5px 0;\n        }\n        .z_loading1 {\n            color: #999;\n            font-size: 12px;\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 5px 0;\n        }\n\n        .z_loading em {\n            background: url(https://cdn.p.yueyouxs.com/static/prod/yygowap/common/image/loading.png) no-repeat;\n            -webkit-background-size: 12px 12px;\n            display: inline-block;\n            width: 12px;\n            height: 12px;\n            margin-right: 10px;\n            -webkit-animation: rotate 1s linear infinite;\n        }\n\n        @-webkit-keyframes rotate {\n            from {\n                -webkit-transform: rotate(0);\n            }\n            to {\n                -webkit-transform: rotate(360deg);\n            }\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n\n<div class=\"header_wrap\">\n    <div class=\"header flex dec_line show\">\n        <div class=\"icon_back\"></div>\n        <div class=\"flex_item\">\n            <div style=\"display: block; text-align: center;padding-top: 15px;font-weight: 400;font-size: 16px;\">\n                <h3>搜索结果</h3>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"icon_home\" onclick=\"gotoPage('/')\"></div>\n    </div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"v-list\">\n    \n    <div class=\"v-list-item flex\" onclick=\"newWebView('/b/229093.html', '', '')\">\n        <div class=\"v-cover\">\n            <img class=\"v-cover-img\" src=\"https://cdn.p.yueyouxs.com/wap/229093/c6b23632fa2e3ea7d740305352f5d9eb.jpg\">\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"v-info flex-item flexcol-justify\">\n            <div class=\"v-content\">\n                <div class=\"v-title\">灵破苍穹</div>\n                <div class=\"v-intro\">一个从青叶小镇走出来的少年，偶然机会解除体内封印，从此文能一念惊天地，武能一掌碎山河。\r\n灵武兼修，踏遍诸天万界，踩踏无数天才，无数强者倒在了他的脚下！</div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"v-other flex-v-end\">\n                <div class=\"v-author\">心跳的瞬间&nbsp; &nbsp;</div>\n                <div class=\"v-words flex-item\">500.55 万字</div>\n                <div class=\"v-group flex\">\n                    <div class=\"border-1px base-label\">玄幻奇幻</div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n    \n    <div class=\"v-list-item flex\" onclick=\"newWebView('/b/236324.html', '', '')\">\n        <div class=\"v-cover\">\n            <img class=\"v-cover-img\" src=\"https://cdn.p.yueyouxs.com/wap/236324/07e7dc57ce7b752727dbfa05aa36c6c4.jpg\">\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"v-info flex-item flexcol-justify\">\n            <div class=\"v-content\">\n                <div class=\"v-title\">破天</div>\n                <div class=\"v-intro\">&#34;本已站在世界巅峰的神级人物，却因为一个古朴的戒指，成为异世界一个药师家族的废物公子。隐忍的锋芒，广博的学识，惊天的才学，高绝的曲艺！\n万年的轮回是因为某种阴谋？还是真真正正的一种巧合？\n顺我者强，逆我者亡，红尘滚滚，天地苍茫，看我如何一剑刺破天芒！&#34;</div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"v-other flex-v-end\">\n                <div class=\"v-author\">青铜&nbsp; &nbsp;</div>\n                <div class=\"v-words flex-item\">322.52 万字</div>\n                <div class=\"v-group flex\">\n                    <div class=\"border-1px base-label\">玄幻奇幻</div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n    \n    <div class=\"v-list-item flex\" onclick=\"newWebView('/b/227310.html', '', '')\">\n        <div class=\"v-cover\">\n            <img class=\"v-cover-img\" src=\"https://cdn.p.yueyouxs.com/wap/227310/6a335964002fc67b66ab72d32cc44fe6.jpg\">\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"v-info flex-item flexcol-justify\">\n            <div class=\"v-content\">\n                <div class=\"v-title\">龙游苍穹</div>\n                <div class=\"v-intro\">少年游龙，身世隐秘；十年隐忍，从未放弃！ 战雷家，解镇危，出蟠龙，创龙盟，坚毅少年闯天下！ 探黑石，进圣光，怀苍生，建帝国，痴情少年有傲魂！ 脚踏九州，声振寰宇；九鼎齐聚，龙游苍穹。 邪魔来袭生灵毁，守护之战惊天地！ 经此一役，幸存万民皆呼己为：龙的传人！</div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"v-other flex-v-end\">\n                <div class=\"v-author\">流风回雪&nbsp; &nbsp;</div>\n                <div class=\"v-words flex-item\">176.98 万字</div>\n                <div class=\"v-group flex\">\n                    <div class=\"border-1px base-label\">玄幻奇幻</div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n    \n    <div class=\"v-list-item flex\" onclick=\"newWebView('/b/229057.html', '', '')\">\n        <div class=\"v-cover\">\n            <img class=\"v-cover-img\" src=\"https://cdn.p.yueyouxs.com/wap/229057/26a69552e4363e78707daa950fbe0cc2.jpg\">\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"v-info flex-item flexcol-justify\">\n            <div class=\"v-content\">\n                <div class=\"v-title\">星核斗天</div>\n                <div class=\"v-intro\">“什么，你说道德经没用。”\r\n    “我告诉你，用什么东西跟我换我都不换。”秦天如是说，他发现道德经不在只是一篇古文那么简单\r\n    ……\r\n    地球青年秦天来到了星核世界，觉醒原核，他发现人们都是一个原核，而他自己却身负两个原核……\r\n    煅经骨，九星圆，真核动，神冲天。\r\n    这是一个异常残酷的世界，异常凶险的世界，也是一个充满机遇的世界，人类修炼，排山倒海，崩山断水。\r\n    男儿自横行，十步杀一人。\r\n    看秦天如何横行在这个世界，过得多姿多彩。</div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"v-other flex-v-end\">\n                <div class=\"v-author\">拎香雪碧&nbsp; &nbsp;</div>\n                <div class=\"v-words flex-item\">361.30 万字</div>\n                <div class=\"v-group flex\">\n                    <div class=\"border-1px base-label\">玄幻奇幻</div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n    \n    <div class=\"v-list-item flex\" onclick=\"newWebView('/b/232679.html', '', '')\">\n        <div class=\"v-cover\">\n            <img class=\"v-cover-img\" src=\"https://cdn.p.yueyouxs.com/wap/232679/0ea5945eae49e3d03a1dd2c117e7708d.jpg\">\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"v-info flex-item flexcol-justify\">\n            <div class=\"v-content\">\n                <div class=\"v-title\">苍穹战神</div>\n                <div class=\"v-intro\">在强者为尊的修行大陆中，少年石洛一度被认定为修炼废材。机缘巧合之下，石洛有幸获得一枚神秘古坠，从此逆转乾坤，傲视苍穹，万战成神！</div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"v-other flex-v-end\">\n                <div class=\"v-author\">光明洛&nbsp; &nbsp;</div>\n                <div class=\"v-words flex-item\">86.58 万字</div>\n                <div class=\"v-group flex\">\n                    <div class=\"border-1px base-label\">玄幻奇幻</div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n    \n</div>\n\n<script>\n\n    $(function () {\n        $(\".icon_back\").on(\"click\",function(){history.back()});\n    });\n\n    var tur = true;\n    var range = 0,\n        maxpage = parseInt( 90 ) + 1,\n        page = 2,\n        totalHeight = 0;\n\n    function loadData() {\n        $(window).scroll(function() {\n            if(tur) {\n                setTimeout(fnscroll, 100);\n                tur = false;\n            }\n        })\n    }\n    loadData();\n\n    function fnscroll() {\n        if(page == -1)\n            return;\n        var scrollHeight = $(window).scrollTop(); \n        totalHeight = parseFloat($(window).height()) + parseFloat(scrollHeight); \n        if(page == maxpage){\n            $('.v-list').append('<div class=\"z_loading1\">已到底</div>');\n            page = -1;\n            return;\n        }\n        if(($(document).height()*2/3) <= totalHeight && page != maxpage) {\n            if($(document).height() <= totalHeight)\n                $('.v-list').append('<div class=\"z_loading\"><em/>正在加载更多数据</div>');\n            $.ajax({\n                async : true,\n                cache : false,\n                type : 'get',\n                url : '/api/book/search?keyword=斗破苍穹' + '&page=' + page,\n                dataType : \"json\",\n                error : function() {},\n                success : function(result) {\n                    $(\".z_loading\").remove();\n                    $(\".z_loading1\").remove();\n                    if(result.code == 0){\n                        if(result.data.length == 0){\n        